I have the Aventura Blu-ray from when they played at madison square garden. But Romeo's Concert on Blu-ray is just "dry" it's boring. Don't get me wrong Romeo has potential but this concert had me bored. When comparing the Aventura to Romeo's concert you can feel the energy among the group and the audience.
One thing that I found weird to my ear was the singing of the second singer sounds strange. One thing I did like from the concert was the quality. It's in HD you can see the smallest detail super clear.
Everything was good.
This is a nice compilation of Romeo Santos Song from Aventura to his solo Career and it comes with many surprises.
